      "description": "We are honored to present this impeccably preserved masterpiece, currently held in a state of absolute refinement. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery condition. Meticulously curated and maintained to the most exacting standards, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire an investment-grade asset. We invite discerning clients to witness this peerless example of automotive engineering and aesthetic integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
