    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically peerless, the rod bearings and double VANOS system have been proactively addressed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, riding on a refined McPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this collector-grade specimen exhibits zero fluid leaks, perfect compression across all cylinders, and an unblemished undercarriage.",
